economic wellbeing of working women they note the aflcio has 
traditionally taken a stand on a wide range of issues including 
civil rights gay rights and school busing 
i would say that the committee probably breaks down almost 
5050 said miller a prochoice member of the abortion panel 
she predicted the aflcio could adopt a prochoice position as long 
as it included language acknowledging the moral and religious views 
of some union members 
kirkland declined to identify his personal position the panels 
chairman william wynn president of the united food and commercial 
