after he was summoned by the coast guard to visit the stricken ship 
and record details of the nations worst oil spill 
he called the tape mental notetaking explaining how he 
accompanied coast guard investigators to the 987foot ship 
the tape which lasted about 10 minutes first showed the ship 
sitting in the darkness its lights glowing the video then 
switched to a period after dawn when the ships deck was more 
visible and a contrast was shown between the gooey black oil on one 
side of the tanker and the clear blue water on the other 
also visible were chunks of ice which the vessel had sought to 
