drinks over a period of about three hours the prosecution 
maintains he was in a bar for about six hours and kept ordering 
vodka on the rocks 
the only point on which all witnesses seem to agree is that 
hazelwood never appeared to be drunk on the exxon valdez even 
delozier who smelled alcohol on him said he did not stagger slur 
his words or appear impaired by alcohol 
