prosecution proposal to call as witnesses experts who claim they 
can tell from listening to tape recordings of a persons voice 
whether they are intoxicated prosecutors want the experts to give 
their opinions about hazelwood from listening to the tape of the 
skipper reporting the exxon valdez grounding to the us coast 
guard 
