they may lose their jobs and some firms have gone bankrupt 
these figures will be multiplied by a significant amount if 
the government does not come to our assistance we are dealing with 
a very dangerous situation he said 
trade officials said imports were dropping by 50 percent as 
companies were being forced to pay import duties in cash 
more than 95 percent of businesses in finland are as small or 
mediumsized employing fewer than 20 people only 02 percent 
employ more than 500 people jarventaus said 
we can survive for just a couple of weeks thats all said 
