times the normal number of new accounts since the bank strike 
offices have been forced to lock their doors for a few hours every 
day to deal with backlogs and massive lines of customers 
its ridiculous our workload has suddenly doubled in some 
cases even trebled or more hopia said something has got to 
give soon we cant take this for very much longer 
