of playing a major role in the government after elections in may 
and in romania some particularly the intellectuals and students 
are concerned that the national salvation front will simply replace 
the communist party and not offer the hopedfor change 
he also cited ethnic strife in romania and yugoslavia as an 
obstacle to reform 
