less than they would have if they had gone to court said sal 
muoio an analyst with gabelli amp co a new york city brokerage 
firm that invests in graphic 
late last year mccaw agreed to buy a controlling interest in 
lin broadcasting corp a new yorkbased cellular telelphone and 
television station operator for 338 billion the deal is 
expected to close in late february 
